reviews.review_text: fix good lovin someone please patch the splice in good lovin'!
pure magic sound quality and show are simply amazing.
Sweet Eyes into Space The Eyes has a slower, more drawn out tenor, but is consistently mellifluous.  No sloppy Jerry here.  Very nice show indeed.
JERRY Black Peter is a Must Listen!!!
might as well give it 5 Smoker! Maybe the best Might as Well.The Eyes>Space>St. Stephen is face melting.

Energy Abounds One of the best, no, no, no, the Best performance in the midwest ever unless you can count the Alpine 89 shows of Downhill legend. There is more energy abounding here than ever before or after, I was at this show and Jerry Garcia was right on cue to open up his bag of tr trcks way beyond belief! You must here the high octane dead play all of the fast songs well fast and the slow songs...SLOW.
